{
  "stem": "11797.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one time I went over to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, Sergeant Schrader, my father is one of the best tailors in-- in Radom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's a woman's tailor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took up tailoring in-- I mean, he learned tailoring in Buenos Aires, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was in Argentina.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he came back from Argentina, you know, and he knew all these fashions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He knew design.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He knows how to make-- tell me, perhaps you have a place for him, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Please, help him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says, I'll see what I can do about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he never said not a word.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He never said to me, I'm going to pick him up, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'll take him or bring him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Never said nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then-- then about-- this was going on about-- when I was there, it must have been about, oh, a month later, the-- they called the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE] means, you know, they took out the Jews, you know, on the street in 1942, mid '42.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I can't remember the month exactly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I think it was in June or July.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When the Germans-- about 5 o'clock in the morning, you know-- knocked on our door-- it was loud.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Rouse, rouse.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, oh, there was all noise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We saw blood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had a-- like a rail coming down the steps, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We lived on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we heard, rouse, rouse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there were-- whoever went slow was beaten with the butt from the rifle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And if anyone was pregnant, they shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We saw-- it's the first time I saw people actually being physically shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I never saw it in my life that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I saw-- they threw kids out from the windows.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
